com.atakmap.android.maps.selector

Class MapItemList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.maps.selector.MapItemList

  • public final class MapItemList
extends java.lang.Object
    A displayable list of map items for selection and filtering purposes Basic usage is to call setItems(Collection) with a non-empty list and then show() to display the list in a drop-down.
